This plugin allow show user image/picture/avatar aside preferences/logout buttons.
# Installation (EN)
 * Uncompress the archive to the `<GLPI_ROOT>/plugins/useravatar` directory
 * Navigate to the Configuration > Plugins page,
 * Install and activate the plugin.
